## Development

```bash
# Clone and setup
git clone https://github.com/GLINCKER/glin-profanity
cd glin-profanity/packages/py
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Testing
pytest
pytest --cov=glin_profanity

# Code quality
black glin_profanity tests
isort glin_profanity tests
mypy glin_profanity
ruff check glin_profanity tests
```

